50|$|Two short {{arms are}} set to form 90 degree angles against a third, longer drawing edge. Pins are placed near {{the edges of the}} <b>drawing</b> <b>surface</b> and serve as pivots for the arms. Pin {{placement}} is equidistant and symmetric across the horizontal line. A third centrolinead could be used to construct 3-point perspective.|$|R
