30|$|The Intuous® Wacom Pro {{multitouch}} tablet {{was used}} to gather the gestures {{as one of the}} tests. The one tablet was shared between the two test rooms due to cost. The Wacom is the go-to <b>drawing</b> <b>surface</b> for artists due to its pressure sensitivity. The Pro has a physical size of 19.1 × 12.5 inches; however, the Pro active area (sensitive to finger touch) was 12.8 × 8.0 (i.e., a 15.1 -inch diagonal).|$|R
